  Marked unstable on mips.

  01 Dec 2007; Markus Rothe <corsair@gentoo.org> libmcs-0.5.0.ebuild:
  Stable on ppc64

  29 Oct 2007; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> libmcs-0.6.0.ebuild:
  Add ~alpha wrt #196169, thanks to Tobias Klausmann for testing

  23 Oct 2007; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> libmcs-0.5.0.ebuild:
  Stable for HPPA too (audacious).

  22 Oct 2007; Roy Marples <uberlord@gentoo.org> libmcs-0.6.0.ebuild:
  Keyworded #x86-fbsd, #196169.

  18 Oct 2007; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> libmcs-0.4.1.ebuild:
  alpha stable, thanks to Tobias Klausmann for testing

  17 Oct 2007; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org> libmcs-0.4.1.ebuild,
  libmcs-0.5.0.ebuild, libmcs-0.6.0.ebuild:
  Add missing dependency on >=dev-libs/libmowgli-0.4.0 as reported by Jeffrey
  Gardner <je_fro@gentoo.org>, bug #196169. Dropped alpha, mips & x86-fbsd
  keywords.

